      "rawType": "P618.2'",
      "required": false,
      "pointerTo": 618.2,
      "helpText": "This is the current team assigned to work with the patient.  When this field is blank this indicates that the patient was been transferred out of the ward or the patient was been discharged.  The CURRENT TEAM field is used to activate the SET and KILL of the following cross-references: \"CP\", \"AC\", \"ACP\", \"ACR\" and \"AWC\". ",
